## Quick Reference: Phase Gates

| Phase | Gate | Condition to proceed |
|-------|------|---------------------|
| 1. Requirements | Gate 1 | User confirms requirements summary |
| 2. ASCII Mockup | Gate 2 | User approves the layout wireframe |
| 3. Generate TWB | — | Automatic after Gate 2 |
| 4. Validate | — | `validate_twb()` outputs `Validation PASSED` |
| 5. Handoff & Iterate | — | Deliver to user; self-learn from user fixes |
| 6. Knowledge Capture | — | Document all learnings in skill references |
